{"article_id":"u2UviMU6oxd7DNt5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Warning of serious repercussions for the economy and the military","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"if Congress fails to halt the next round of $ 85 billion in budget cuts next month ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"President Obama on Tuesday called for replacing the automatic spending \" sequesters \" with a vague mix of smaller cuts and more tax increases .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"At a time","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"when many top Republicans have said","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"the cuts should take effect ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. Obama ' s call renews the battle over spending","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"that has dominated Washington for the past two years ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"but which seemed to cool after the January deal","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that raised taxes across the board .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The president said","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"he would like another big tax reform","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that targets the wealthy ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"cutting deductions and loopholes ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"but said","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"at the very least Congress should avert the sequester ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"which he called an avoidable self-inflicted economic wound .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"\" If they can ' t get a bigger package done by the time","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"the sequester is scheduled to go into effect ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"then I believe","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"they should at least pass a smaller package , \"","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"\" There is no reason","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that the jobs of thousands of Americans","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"who work in national security or education or clean energy","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"- not to mention the growth of the entire economy -","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"should be put in jeopardy . \"","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"His offer is a rehash of proposals","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"he has made","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to end tax breaks and lower projected increases in health care spending ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"though the White House has yet to lay out a full list of deductions","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"it wants Congress to target .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Even before Mr. Obama spoke ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Republicans were rejecting his offer .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"House Speaker John A. Boehner , Ohio Republican , issued a statement","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"it was the president","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"who came up with the sequester idea .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"He also said","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"House Republicans have passed two bills","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"to avert the sequesters ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"so Mr. Obama must lay out his own specific plan .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Still smarting from his \" fiscal cliff \" deal with Democrats","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"in which Republicans agreed to increase taxes","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"without spending cuts ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"the speaker made it clear","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that he was ruling out any need","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"to increase taxes further .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"\" President Obama first proposed the sequester","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"and insisted","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"it become law .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Republicans have twice voted to replace these arbitrary cuts with common-sense cuts and reforms","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that protect our national defense , \"","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"\" We believe","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"there is a better way","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"to reduce the deficit ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"but Americans do not support sacrificing real spending cuts for more tax hikes .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"\" The president ' s sequester should be replaced with spending cuts and reforms","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that will start us on the path","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"to balancing the budget in 10 years , \"","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell , Kentucky Republican , rebuked Mr. Obama","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"for lecturing Congress about the need","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"to avoid the cuts","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"he proposed .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"\" If Democrats have ideas for smarter cuts ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"they should bring them up for debate , \"","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"\" But the American people will not support more tax hikes in place of the meaningful spending reductions","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"both parties already agreed to","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"and the president signed into law . \"","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"Mr. McConnell also criticized Mr. Obama for failing to submit a budget by the statutory deadline this year .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" The clock is ticking .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"It ' s time","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"to get serious , \"","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"he added .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"The White House first came up with the idea of the arbitrary , across-the-board spending cuts during budget talks in summer 2011 as a way","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"to pressure Democrats and Republicans in Congress into coming up with their own spending cut plan","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"to reduce the deficit over the next decade .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"But partisan Washington gridlock quickly took hold","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"and a supercommittee of lawmakers","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"tasked with coming up with a plan","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"to find alternative spending cuts","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"to replace the sequester","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"failed to reach a deal","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"after negotiating for months .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"As the country braced for the cuts to kick in","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"and Washington to tumble off the fiscal cliff Jan. 1 ,","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"lawmakers struck a last-minute deal","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"that shifted the first two months of cuts into future spending bills","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"and replaced the rest with an increase in the way","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"retirement accounts are taxed .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Still , the deal postponed another $ 85 billion in cuts to March 1","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"- a way","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"to buy more time","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"to find alternative sources of revenue .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"The Pentagon in recent weeks has grown increasingly pessimistic about the chances","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"of avoiding the cuts ,","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"and the branches of the military have issued memos","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"outlining what programs and sections would be hit hardest .","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"Washington think tanks and policy centers have warned repeatedly of the havoc","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"that the cuts could wreak on the economy .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"The Bipartisan Policy Center has estimated","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"that 1 million jobs could be lost this year and next as a direct result of the spending cuts ,","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"and defense industry analysts say","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"that number could rise to 2 million this year alone .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"The president made his plea","depth":3},{"id":108,"text":"as Senate Democrats were meeting in Annapolis for their annual retreat .","depth":3},{"id":109,"text":"Mr. Obama is scheduled to address the group Wednesday .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":219,"left":216,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":186,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":119,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":112,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":111,"right":2,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":114,"right":117,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":114,"left":3,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":117,"left":6,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":7,"right":115,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":135,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":122,"right":134,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":10,"right":121,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":11,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":124,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":14,"right":123,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":128,"right":132,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":21,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":125,"right":126,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nu